node.text:
Italy is by far one of the most beautiful places i ever been... [ & i been everywhere ] this trip we did Paris, France...then headed to Italy...Amalfi Coast 😍, Capri, & Rome. So thankful for this life i live 💖🙏🏾 the only other place I’ve seen with views this good is Santorini Greece..did that a few years back 🙂✈️ i keep saying I’m going to start blogging when i travel but I’m literally so caught up in the moment that i forget to get the content 😩 should i??? 
#travel #blackgirltravel  #travelgram
